channel.title: Need to fix your 377/317 cache? Ripped apart 377 cache in here
channel.description:
Alright, well, i have seen SOO many clients with broken cache's etc. I have ripped apart the deob 377 cache, and everything that came out of it is in this .rar download, the maps, models, sound-effects. No pictures though, since you can do that through Tom's Cache Suite.
PIC: [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/22dr29.png[/img]
DL: http://www.mediafire.com/?0jyehnzygyc
NOTE: The models are not gzipped, they are just str8 from the cache as a .dat, so dont try to load them into your cache until then.
